de.esoco.ewt.layout

Class GroupLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.ewt.layout.GenericLayout
      • de.esoco.ewt.layout.TwoLayerLayout
        • de.esoco.ewt.layout.GroupLayout

  • public class GroupLayout
extends TwoLayerLayout
    A layout that groups components with an optional title/caption. The title must be set in the container's style data with the name StandardProperties.TITLE.
